This file is used by Tomcat for database connection DataSource configuration.
Set the proper attributes and put this file in:
<tomcat_dir>/conf/Catalina/localhost/

Note: The file name should be the same name as the web application .war file.
      E.g. If the web application is called ErgoRR-web-war.war then 
           this file should be named ErgoRR-web-war.xml
-->